PartBuilder<T> Class

In this Article

Extends the PartBuilder class to allow the use of expressions to select members.

Syntax

Declaration

public class PartBuilder<T> : System.ComponentModel.Composition.Registration.PartBuilder

Type Parameters

The type of the target.
